ISLAMABAD, Jul 15 (APP):Deputy Prime Minister Muhammad Ishaq Dar on Monday extended his congratulations to Dr. Arzu Rana Deuba on his  appointment as the foreign minister of Nepal.
In an official statement on his X account, Dar, who also serves as the foreign minister, conveyed his intention to collaborate closely with Arzu Rana for enhancing bilateral relations and fostering mutually beneficial cooperation between Pakistan and Nepal.
